    "title": "[Kernel] Support TRTLLM GEN NVFP4 MoE for non-512-aligned hidden dims via weight padding",
    "user": {
      "login": "danielafrimi",
      "id": 45691845,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ1NjkxODQ1",
