    "body": "## Summary\r\n- Relaxes `_supports_shape` check from `hidden_dim % 512` to always True or TRTLLM NVFP4 MoE kernel - we pad in load time the weights to enable running this kernel (might cause perf gain for some shapes - added a warninig for this)\r\n- Zero-pads MoE weights to next multiple of 256 (no need 512 alignment) at load time . \r\n- Runtime activation padding/output slicing handled by existing MoE runner infrastructure — no custom padding in `apply()`\r\n- Fixes modular `apply()` autotuning bug: writes zeros to output buffer instead of returning unused value\r\n\r\nOn https://huggingface.co/nvidia/NVIDIA-Nemotron-3-Nano-30B-A3B-NVFP4\r\n\r\n**lm-eval:**\r\nGSM8K (reasoning off):\r\nTRTLLM: flexible: 0.8597 ; strict: 0.8446\r\nCutlass:  flexible: 0.8658 ; strict: 0.8491\r\n\r\n\r\n**Benchmark**\r\n\r\nCommand\r\n```\r\npython -m vllm.entrypoints.cli.main bench serve \\\r\n  --backend openai-chat \\\r\n  --endpoint /v1/chat/completions \\\r\n  --model nvidia/NVIDIA-Nemotron-3-Nano-30B-A3B-NVFP4 \\\r\n  --trust-remote-code \\\r\n  --seed 0 \\\r\n  --dataset-name random \\\r\n  --random-input-len 1024 \\\r\n  --random-output-len 8192 \\\r\n  --num-prompts 96 \\\r\n  --max-concurrency 32 \\\r\n  --request-rate inf \\\r\n  --temperature 0\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nMetric | Cutlass (previous) | TRTLLM (new default) | Delta\r\n-- | -- | -- | --\r\nBenchmark duration (s) | 112.64 | 92.35 | -20.29 (-18.02%)\r\nRequest throughput (req/s) | 0.85 | 1.04 | +0.19 (+22.35%)\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s) | 6,981.92 | 8,515.42 | +1,533.50 (+21.96%)\r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s) | 7,386.00 | 9,357.00 | +1,971.00 (+26.69%)\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s) | 7,854.66 | 9,579.85 | +1,725.19 (+21.96%)\r\nMean TTFT (ms) | 799.33 | 651.69 | -147.64 (-18.47%)\r\nMedian TTFT (ms) | 544.43 | 654.19 | +109.76 (+20.16%)\r\nP99 TTFT (ms) | 1,562.49 | 1,042.71 | -519.78 (-33.27%)\r\nMean TPOT (ms) | 4.49 | 3.68 | -0.81 (-18.04%)\r\nMedian TPOT (ms) | 4.51 | 3.63 | -0.88 (-19.51%)\r\nP99 TPOT (ms) | 4.57 | 3.94 | -0.63 (-13.79%)\r\nMean ITL (ms) | 4.49 | 3.68 | -0.81 (-18.04%)\r\nMedian ITL (ms) | 4.48 | 3.63 | -0.85 (-18.97%)\r\nP99 ITL (ms) | 4.79 | 4.04 | -0.75 (-15.66%)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Test plan\r\n- [x] Unit tests for padding logic (`test_trtllm_nvfp4_hidden_dim_padding.py`)\r\n- [x] Verified serving Upcoming model with `--moe-backend flashinfer_trtllm` on Blackwell\r\n- [x] Verified serving NemotronH 120B (hidden_size=4096, no padding needed) unchanged",
